+# Permission Maze Implementation Plan
+
+> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.
+
+**Goal:** Build a document management API with users, hierarchical folders, documents, sharing permissions, and activity logging.
+
+**Architecture:** Express.js REST API with in-memory storage using Maps. Middleware handles auth token validation. Permissions cascade from folders to documents, with the most permissive role winning when multiple grants exist.
+
+**Tech Stack:** Express.js, TypeScript, Vitest + Supertest for testing
+
+---
+
+### Task 1: Project Scaffolding - Types and Storage
